  "content_id": "c5b5c0f5-05cf-476d-950e-6d423ab352cf",
  "description": "Find training courses to qualify to become an approved driving instructor (ADI)",
  "details": {
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introduction": "<p>Find training courses to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>qualify to become an approved driving instructor (<abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>prepare for your <a href=\"/adi-standards-check\"><abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> standards check</a>\n</li>\n  <li>improve your skills as part of your <a href=\"/approved-driving-instructor-adi-development\">continuing professional development</a> (<abbr title=\"continuing professional development\">CPD</abbr>)</li>\n</ul>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p>The trainers are on the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency’s official register of driving instructor training - which is sometimes called <abbr title=\"official register of driving instructor training\">ORDIT</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a different process to <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/articles/how-become-approved-driving-instructor-adi\">become an ADI in Northern Ireland.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "place_type": "driving-instructor-training"
  },
